        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Image Flip or Rotate. ",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            206,
            334,
            364,
            349
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如果使用单图像工具来翻转或旋转输入图像，则输出图像的根空间将反映翻转或旋转。",
        "bbox": [
            206,
            351,
            850,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/466e4472c7534017e777e5074d23037d8339b785da9de6dcf9e2ca629fe5a858.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            210,
            394,
            505,
            558
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/0f537a932b71e45265539bdf78cafeee0c31018a730ab7e6c2916126f44694c8.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            569,
            388,
            900,
            596
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "CogCopyRegionTool的行为类似于仿射变换(如上所述)。输出图像的根空间反映了输入图像的根空间与被复制区域之间的转换。",
        "bbox": [
            205,
            648,
            850,
            683
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/61c0da89d7953e882ea8007fa4b1e8d28d94a12fe0a26a967006ae6a5539a447.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
        "image_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            218,
            690,
            559,
            864
        ],
        "page_idx": 7
    },
    {
        "type": "image",
        "img_path": "images/3d71fefdd612c069653bb00fcd8b8a1916461b985d1cb9429f808fb101b86f55.jpg",
        "image_caption": [],
